    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《武士幸存者》是一款类吸血鬼幸存者的肉鸽类砍杀游戏。你的年龄会不断增长，同时需要杀死恶灵、学习技能，成长为最强大的武士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/58bdadb3e9034d8e7ef20a3c3aa9b479.webp?t=1749040885\" width=635 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/bc3ad161118f8167b663d555e6a506df.poster.avif?t=1749040885\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/bc3ad161118f8167b663d555e6a506df.webm?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/bc3ad161118f8167b663d555e6a506df.mp4?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你背叛了自己的宗族，并背负了一生与恶灵为战的诅咒。你在修成正果之前会持续变老，同时你的剑术也会越来越精湛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/58bdadb3e9034d8e7ef20a3c3aa9b479.webp?t=1749040885\" width=635 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/f620b1343222562ee7cdd76cb7fe1937.poster.avif?t=1749040885\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/f620b1343222562ee7cdd76cb7fe1937.webm?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/f620b1343222562ee7cdd76cb7fe1937.mp4?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   数小时激烈的砍杀与生存！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   多达 26 种独特的攻击方式，互相配合能产生威力惊人的协同效应！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   敌人种类丰富有趣，具有独特机制！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   多张不同风格地图，每一张都有着特定的敌人与机制！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   多种武器和攻击技能会逐步解锁！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   可不断提升等级，且通关后还能继续游玩！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   体验游戏专属的日本中世纪风格音乐！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   此外，还有许许多多丰富有趣的玩法待您探索！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/58bdadb3e9034d8e7ef20a3c3aa9b479.webp?t=1749040885\" width=635 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/3574239fc82313f1550ab1f96b9d02a0.poster.avif?t=1749040885\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/3574239fc82313f1550ab1f96b9d02a0.webm?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317960/extras/3574239fc82313f1550ab1f96b9d02a0.mp4?t=1749040885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Samurai Illustration by Toriotto</p>",
